{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redsi/ es eſmu to Ralleju raddijs/ kas tahs Ohgles Uggu- ni uſpuhſch/ weenu Rihfu pa- darra par tawu Darbu/ ir to Samaitataju eſinn es raddijs Samaitatchanas pehz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſam Rihkam/ kas prett tew tohp padarrihts/ ne- labbi iſdohſees/ un tn pasuddi- naft wiſſu Mehli/ kas prett tewi Sohdá zettahs. Schi irr ta ee- mantojama Teefa ta KUNGA Kalpu/ un winnu Taifniba irr no mannim/ takka tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta LV. Nodalla.\nEsaijs eekſch ta KUNGA Krislus Wahrda (Jhpaſchibas) kafauz ikweenn pee tahs Schchlafibas Waſfiba ta Ewangelsjuma- 1. To bes Naudas/ bes Nopelna zur winna Schehlaſtibu ween usneamt: 2. Pamahza/ ka teem buhs Krisſtu pee Laika meſlecht: 6. Lihosina to Deewa Wahrda Sluddinaschanu weenam augligam Leetum un Eneegam: 10.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "All tad/ wiſſi juhs Js- Atwihkuschee/ nahzcet pee Luhdens/ un juhs kam Naudas newaid/ nahzeet/ pir- zeet un ehdeet/ nahzeet un pir- zeet bes Naudas un bes Maksas/ Wihsu un Peenu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kapehz noswerrat juhs Nandu par to/ kas Maise ne irr/ un juhsu Darbu par to/ no ka ne warr pee-chſtees? Klausajt man ar labbu Klautſchannu/ un ehdeet to labbu/ tad juhsu Dwebfele eekſch Tawkumeem gardi preeza- fees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Greesect ſchurp juhsu An- i/ un nahzcet pee mannis/ itau-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "fajt/ tad juhsu Dwebfele dsih- wohs/ jo es darrischu ar jume weenu muhschigu Derribu/ (dohdams jums) tahs peetiz- zigas Apschehloſchanas Dah- wida.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redsi/ es eſmu winnu teem Laudim par Leezineeku ee- zehlis/ par Wirfneeku un Wal- ditaju to Zautu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi/ tn ſauksi Paga- nus/ ko tn ne pasinnt/ un Lau- dis/ kas tewi ne pasinne/ tezzehe pee tewim/ ta KUNGA taawa Deewa deht/ jo tas irr tewi pa- gohdinajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Meflejeet to KUNGU/ ka- wehr tas atrastiss irr/ peefau- zeet winnu/ kanchr tas tuwu trraid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lat tas Besdeewigajs pa- mett jawu Zettu/un tas Launa- darritajs jawas Dohnas/ un at- greeschahs pee ta KUNGA/ tad tas pahr winnu apschehloſees/ un pee muhsu Deewa/ jo pee winna irr dauds Peedohſchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo mannas Dohnas ne irr juhsas Dohnas/ un juhsu Zetti ne irr manni Zetti/ fakka tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo itt ka ta Debbes ang- flaka irr neka ta Semme/ ta irr manni Zetti angflaki neka juhsu Zetti/ un mannas Dohnas neka juhsas Dohnas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo itt ka tas Leetus un Sneegs no Debbes friht/ un turp ne atgreeschahs/ bet klappi- na to Semmi/ uu darra winnu angli-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
